as2flexlogger ( http://github.com/alechill/as2flexlogger )

as2flexlogger is an ActionScript2 port of the Flex logging API. 

Use the same Flex logging API you are familiar when working on projects which rely on ActionScript 2, targeting Flash Lite for example.

